name: Goma Handbag Flamenco
description:
(KM13)

Funky handbag made from car tyre inner tubes. Its unique design is inspired by the style of a Spanish flamenco dress. It suits every occasion, from being very dressy when you're going to the theatre or functional when you go to work. 

The inside compartment contains a practical zipped pocket and is lined with nylon. Removable strap.

Lining colour options:
Pink, Mustard, Petrol

30cm x 37cm x 7cm

Designed in Berlin by Ainhoa Salgueiro. Ethically and sustainably produced in Vietnam.

FREE SHIPPING AUSTRALIA WIDE.

name: VuerichB sunglasses Rad n°393 (Skateboard)
description:
(RAD393)

No pair of sunnies the Vuerich brothers create from recycled skateboard is the same, because every skateboard is different and leads to a different combination of colours. Logically, this piece with the serial n° 393 is absolutely unique. 

The flexibility and strength of maple wood as well as an extremely skillful manufacturing process guarantee uncompromisingly high quality and impressive details. They are very solid, yet they only weigh 26g.

The high quality Carl Zeiss Cat. 3 CR 39 lenses provide 100% UVA/UVB protection. The frame can easily be turned into prescription eyeglasses, to do so speak to your local optician and drop us an email for detailed instructions.

Our size rating for n° 393: Small. 
Large size frame at 140mm width / Nose bridge 21mm / Lens width 48mm / Temple length 140mm / Temple Aperture: S

Comes with a protective pouch and cloth.

Designed by Gianni and Baptiste Vuerich. Made in Barcelona/Spain.

FREE SHIPPING AUSTRALIA WIDE.

Returns policy: Full refund if glasses are returned within 7 days in original condition and packaging.

name: ad:acta Satchel Dienstweg blk
description:
(1002 - black)

The base for this stunning satchel is a castoff A4 ringbinder, which the designers free from its ring clamp, and apply a protective coating to guard against inclement weather.

The bag is crafted with hand-stitched black leather and closes with a zipper. Its fine black fabric lining, adjustable shoulder strap and three interior pockets round out its classy finishing and make it the perfect companion for work or leisure. Each bag maintains the original folder’s mottled patina as a badge of honor.

Easily fits A4 documents, a 13'' laptop or iPad.

32cm x 29cm x 9cm

Designed by Carsten Fichtel and Tobias Förtsch. Made in Germany.

FREE SHIPPING AUSTRALIA WIDE.
